{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b95f7a4585","title":"关于朝鲜主力战场的新闻报道的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"93c21f9724","index":0,"year":1950,"month":11,"day":17,"articleId":"b95f7a4585"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"7dd26a5ad0","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b95f7a4585","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东写给中共中央宣传部副部长、中央人民政府新闻总署署长胡乔木的信。"}],"contents":[{"id":"1b28a04534","type":"title","text":"关于朝鲜主力战场的新闻报道的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b95f7a4585"},{"id":"7dd26a5ad0","type":"paragraph","text":"乔木：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b95f7a4585"},{"id":"2681e6bb62","type":"paragraph","text":"一切有关朝鲜主力战场的新闻，都应将朝鲜人民军与中国人民志愿部队联在一起说，不应只提人民军而不提中国人民志愿部队，如“新华社十五日讯”那样，这样的电讯发到前线和全国都没有好处。关于朝鲜消息，塔斯社的一些不关重要的电讯都不应转发，新华社应自己派人去采访发电，或在北京根据内部情报自己写电讯","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b95f7a4585"},{"id":"00ba42cbcd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b95f7a4585"},{"id":"de0dfdc516","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b95f7a4585"},{"id":"a57d3e23c5","type":"paragraph","text":"报纸应写社论鼓励志愿军。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b95f7a4585"},{"id":"29c770c1cc","type":"paragraph","text":"《参考消息》上，无根据地乱安题目，帮助美国人热吓中国人，也应加以整顿。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b95f7a4585"}],"page":{"id":"7b2d3fab90","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"b95f7a4585","start":376,"end":376}}}},"__N_SSG":true}